** linux: linux is an open source operating system that is widely used in computer, servers and other devices.It is known for its stability,security and flexibility.**


**difference between window and linux ?**
linux                             window 
It is a open source.              It is close source.
It is free of cost.               It requires licensing fees.
It is more secure.                It is not more secure.
Highly customized.                Limited customized.
More helpful for programmer       On the  other hand  we can use the window for gaming. 



